gavad Gita| ]]\n[[Category:Hindu texts]]\n[[Category:Vaishnava texts]]\n[[Category:Gaudiya Vaishnavism]]\n[[Category:Mahabharata]]\n[[Category:Sanskrit texts]]\n[[Category:Kurukshetra]]\n[[Category:Krishna]]\n[[Category:Works of unknown authorship]]\n[[Category:Ancient yoga texts]]\n[[Category:Dialogues]]\n", "name_user": "117.195.200.85", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eOnline sources)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhagavad_Gita"}
{"title_page": "1995 MAC Men's Basketball Tournament", "text_new": "{{short description|Postseason championship basketball tournament for the Mid-American Conference}}\n{{Infobox NCAA Basketball Conference Tournament\n| Year           = 1995\n| Conference     = Mid-American Conference\n| Gender         = Men's\n| Image          = \n| ImageSize      = \n| Caption        = \n| Teams          = 8\n| Arena          = [[Savage Arena]]\n| City           = [[Toledo, Ohio]]\n| Champions      = [[Ball State Cardinals men's basketball|Ball State]]\n| TitleCount     = 6th\n| Coach          = [[Ray McCallum]]\n| CoachCount     = 1st\n| MVP            = [[Steve Payne (basketball)|Steve Payne]]\n| MVPTeam        = Ball State\n| Attendance     =\n| OneTopScorer   = \n| TwoTopScorers  =\n| TopScorer      = \n| TopScorerTeam  = \n| TopScorer2     =\n| TopScorer2Team =\n| Points         = \n| Television     = \n}}\n{{1994\u201395 Mid-American Conference men's basketball standings}}\n\nThe '''1995 [[MAC Men's Basketball Tournament]]''', a part of the [[1994\u201395 NCAA Division I men's basketball season]], took place at [[Savage Arena]] in [[Toledo, Ohio]]. Its winner received the [[Mid-American Conference]]'s [[automatic bid]] to the [[1995 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament|1995 NCAA Tournament]]. It was a [[single-elimination tournament]] with three rounds and the top eight MAC teams invited to participate. No teams received [[bye (sports)|byes]] in the tournament. [[Miami RedHawks men's basketball|Miami]] received the number one seed in the tournament.\n\n== Tournament ==\n===Seeds===\n# Miami\n# Ohio\n# Eastern Michigan\n# Ball State\n# Bowling Green\n# Toledo\n# Western Michigan\n# Kent State\n\n=== Bracket ===\n{{8TeamBracket\n| RD1-seed1='''1'''\n| RD1-team1='''[[Miami RedHawks men's basketball|Miami]]'''\n| RD1-score1='''77'''\n| RD1-seed2=8\n| RD1-team2=[[Kent State Golden Flashes men's basketball|Kent State]]\n| RD1-score2=49\n| RD1-seed3='''4'''\n| RD1-team3='''[